Interface ICarbonRampable

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    CarbonTalon

    public interface ICarbonRampable
    Interface to allow objects to be rampable. To be used with CarbonRampCommand, and any motor controllers we'd like to use. This expands the ramp's compatibility beyond just the CarbonTalon.
    Author:
    Nick Mosher, Team 1829 Carbonauts Captain
